text: Tarakan volcano is located in Indonesia's Halmahera islands, near the shore of Galela Bay north east of Dukono volcano. Tarakan consists of two large cinder cones, namely Tarakan Lamo (large Tarakan) and Tarakan Itji (small Tarakan). ==References== Category:Mountains of Indonesia Category:Volcanoes of Halmahera Category:Pyroclastic cones Category:Maluku Islands
title: Mount Tarakan
